# ğŸ’» Technical View

| Feature                   | **NAT Adapter**            | **NAT Network**                                                     |
| ------------------------- | -------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Internet Access           | âœ… Yes                      | âœ… Yes                                                               |
| VM â†” Host Communication   | âŒ No                       | âŒ No (by default)                                                   |
| VM â†” VM Communication     | âŒ No                       | âœ… Yes                                                               |
| External LAN Access to VM | âŒ No                       | âŒ No                                                                |
| Use Case                  | Single VM ko internet dena | Multiple VMs ek lab environment me internet + apas me communication |

